# BitOS Package Repository
# Format: name  version  description
bit-hello        1.1    BitOS SDK example / hello world script
bit-sysinfo      1.1    Detailed CPU, memory, disk and network info
bit-netinfo      1.1    Network diagnostics - interfaces, routes, connectivity tests
bit-monitor      1.1    Live system monitor with CPU/mem/process view (Ctrl+C to exit)
bit-diskinfo     1.1    Disk and filesystem usage with visual bar charts
bit-update       1.1    Update all installed GitHub packages at once
bit-ps           1.1    Process manager with per-process info and kill support
bit-log          1.1    Log viewer/manager - view, tail, clear system logs
bit-bench        1.1    CPU and memory benchmark tool
bit-files        1.1    File browser with view, find, info, size commands
bit-editor       1.1    Text file editor with vi backend and file browser
bit-net          1.1    Network toolkit - get, dns, ping, scan, speed, trace
bit-backup       1.1    Backup and restore /etc and /home to /var/backup
bit-cron         1.1    Cron job manager - list, add, remove, edit jobs
bit-firewall     1.0    Firewall manager TUI - allow/block ports, view rules, reset
bit-ssl          1.0    TLS certificate generator and HTTPS manager
bit-users        1.0    Full user management TUI - add, delete, passwd, info
bit-containers   1.0    Chroot container manager - create, exec, start, stop
